data.description: Beautifully situated 3 bedroom and 2 bath home for those seeking space, tranquility, and ultimate country lifestyle and rural living. Located off paved road. Offering a perfect blend of comfort with abundant Water Supply with well on the property. Added bonus enitre home is on a filtration system with reverse osmosis system in the kitchen.   The Master bedroom privately situated to one side of the house with large connected bathroom and several frosted windows to let natural sunlight into a relaxing garden tub, with separate walk-in shower. Open concept is good for entertaining.  An office nook off to the side of the kitchen has a built - desk and lots of cabinet storage. Separate laundry room. New laminate wood flooring.
